    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769140/extras/76492324327824aaa9eec8c4d9725ff2.avif?t=1765565043\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769140/extras_big/76492324327824aaa9eec8c4d9725ff2.webp?t=1765565043 width=1560 height=201 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769140/extras/c99b6fbbf02cc2cf1e9e70d1032a2d31.poster.avif?t=1765565043\" width=1170 height=614 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769140/extras/c99b6fbbf02cc2cf1e9e70d1032a2d31.webm?t=1765565043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769140/extras/c99b6fbbf02cc2cf1e9e70d1032a2d31.mp4?t=1765565043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入《MIRAI #167》和乔纳斯的冒险旅程。两位被时间分隔、却灵魂相连的角色。自由切换他们，以发挥各自独特的能力，突破障碍、击败敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769140/extras/384f4715726423c3e2348de607d8553b.avif?t=1765565043\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769140/extras_big/384f4715726423c3e2348de607d8553b.webp?t=1765565043 width=1560 height=201 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769140/extras/61f3285e0967f2a865a65c985e7ab792.poster.avif?t=1765565043\" width=1170 height=614 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769140/extras/61f3285e0967f2a865a65c985e7ab792.webm?t=1765565043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769140/extras/61f3285e0967f2a865a65c985e7ab792.mp4?t=1765565043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用多种方式击败并穿越敌人：近身格斗、反弹子弹、投掷场景中的物体，或运用经典跑酷动作如跳跃、滑行与冲刺，畅快闯关！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769140/extras/3b186ca86a5ff8df865d31b4d4e251da.avif?t=1765565043\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769140/extras_big/3b186ca86a5ff8df865d31b4d4e251da.webp?t=1765565043 width=1560 height=201 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769140/extras/7cd7ce426e4eac004d9d80fb66df2537.poster.avif?t=1765565043\" width=1170 height=614 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769140/extras/7cd7ce426e4eac004d9d80fb66df2537.webm?t=1765565043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769140/extras/7cd7ce426e4eac004d9d80fb66df2537.mp4?t=1765565043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一击就出局？没关系。随心所欲地倒带时间，改正错误，再次出发。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769140/extras/a2236f41c37d23e9fa8b48c98821bc1d.avif?t=1765565043\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769140/extras_big/a2236f41c37d23e9fa8b48c98821bc1d.webp?t=1765565043 width=1560 height=201 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769140/extras/d98901d8ec395c0b826ec4d73a6aae86.poster.avif?t=1765565043\" width=1170 height=614 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769140/extras/d98901d8ec395c0b826ec4d73a6aae86.webm?t=1765565043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769140/extras/d98901d8ec395c0b826ec4d73a6aae86.mp4?t=1765565043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁强大的新技能，并通过动态成长系统强化角色能力，打造符合您游戏风格的玩法体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769140/extras/362119dbac73513633be382094125194.avif?t=1765565043\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769140/extras_big/362119dbac73513633be382094125194.webp?t=1765565043 width=1560 height=201 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769140/extras/4c3f9117e84adf56914f7616ca2a80a5.poster.avif?t=1765565043\" width=1170 height=614 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769140/extras/4c3f9117e84adf56914f7616ca2a80a5.webm?t=1765565043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769140/extras/4c3f9117e84adf56914f7616ca2a80a5.mp4?t=1765565043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一段神秘的故事通过电影般的场景在游戏中自然展开，最终走向令人惊讶且难以预料的结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在智能机器人掌控未来的时代，饱受愧疚折磨的程序员乔纳斯必须直面自己参与创造的机器，因为它们正威胁着人类的生存。由乔纳斯亲手设计的强大时空穿越机器人《MIRAI #167》，从未来被派遣而来阻止他，试图改变历史的进程。</p>",
